Invocation Name: flight deals
des:
Looking for an exciting get-a-way, listen to the the latest airfare deals for flights from major US airports.

Examples:
"Alexa, ask Flight Deals what are today's deals from New York".
"Alexa, ask Flight Deals for deals on Delta".
"Alexa, ask Flight Deals for deals from Seattle".
"Alexa, ask Flight Deals for deals to London".
"Alexa, ask Flight Deals for deals between Seattle and London"
"Alexa, ask Flight Deals to list all cities".
"Alexa, ask Flight Deals for summary of deals".
"Alexa, ask Flight Details for latest ten deals:.
